1. Which of the following is an example of a class?
Choose as many answers as you see fit.


a)A Car class that has a make and model, and that can be driven

b)A Flower class that has a scent

c)A Puppy class that has breed, weight and age, and that can bark

d)A ShoppingCart class that has a cart size and cart value, and that can hold items

e)A Song class that has lyrics

f)None of these are examples of a class.

